{"tid":752510,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關進化論問題","createTime":"2018-07-23T01:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T08:45:06.000Z","uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a887ddb2f116df6133435fbd2b8c4bc1319b80dc","tid":752510,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T01:09:51.000Z","msg":"除咗人類，以前、依家同將來，有無其他物種都係進化成高智慧物種？<br />\n既然人類可以進化成依家咁，係咪其他物種都可以？<br />\n以前既話，恐龍算唔算？<br />\n依家又有無發現有邊啲物種，喺可見將來可以進化成高智慧物種？"},{"pid":"50bb0ccf836b5a987d1be381fdab423b43a87ebf","tid":752510,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"人類由智人物種發展左六萬年先產生文明<br />\n就類近既其他人種都被同化<br />\n現今都無類似既物種 十萬年都應該無除非好似猿人爭霸戰咁"},{"pid":"dfc9bf048dbe3cbe711b6a871f27c5363696e40c","tid":752510,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:32:37.000Z","msg":"有無話點解得人類一種高智慧生物？人類好彩？"},{"pid":"abc16c1e4bf44c423df19971b7e7db6dd23a30ae","tid":752510,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc9bf048dbe3cbe711b6a871f27c5363696e40c","tid":752510,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:32:37.000Z","msg":"有無話點解得人類一種高智慧生物？人類好彩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"概率，為左更好適應環境咁啱好個身體構造慢慢生到咁。"},{"pid":"52bdb0afcd0a9a45f28ce28ce85b47a9e6088c6a","tid":752510,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/000/158/329/9189283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Foriginal%2F000%2F158%2F329%2F9189283.jpg&h=7345b888&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"339434c71e287f9885d0d7886e8345a02db9e809","tid":752510,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc9bf048dbe3cbe711b6a871f27c5363696e40c","tid":752510,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:32:37.000Z","msg":"有無話點解得人類一種高智慧生物？人類好彩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"聽過幾個解釋, 可能係幾樣加起:<br />\n1. 人類開始識用火煮食開始, 蛋白質有助肌肉/腦袋發展<br />\n2. 人有姆指可以製造/使用工具, <br />\n3. 人識得用後腳行步, Free up 雙手使用工具."},{"pid":"ff8d649e0ef216f2d5fb1f021cc196bb6cacd7e4","tid":752510,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"所有野都只係機率<br />\n唔係必然<br />\n<br />\n你問仲有冇其他物種演化做高智慧生物?<br />\n有，但你都唔會見到/知道<br />\n因為演化係講緊要一段好長好長嘅時間"},{"pid":"11779e93df00b2e8452ea5e32a2b630b9e1c5e29","tid":752510,"uid":100766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"你問恐龍算唔算?<br />\n<br />\n其實你今時今日每日都會見到恐龍<br />\n不過你唔知原來伊佢地就係恐龍嘅演化後代黎啫"},{"pid":"b456b62fa49f74edc549a0563fad4c485a4678ca","tid":752510,"uid":64178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc9bf048dbe3cbe711b6a871f27c5363696e40c","tid":752510,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:32:37.000Z","msg":"有無話點解得人類一種高智慧生物？人類好彩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"睇sapiens<br />\n答咗呢個難題"}]}